{"tid":2321542,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友趁得閒搞左壇野係關 NBA","createTime":"2020-12-11T14:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:27:56.000Z","uid":387162,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9281ba88c131e3b5a54d7e569fbacf2601ccd52","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"[代Post] <br />\n是咁的，平時睇 NBA 都會估下邊隊贏，基於馬會係無NBA 賭，自己一個估又有點乏味，心諗不如整壇野係估NBA 賽果，所以就整左佢出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳送門 : <a href=\"https://llclk.com/nba4funhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fllclk.com%2Fnba4funhk%2F&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=9b5cab2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://llclk.com/nba4funhk/</a>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BRZDr47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBRZDr47.png&h=5f964bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩法好簡單，估邊隊贏，有倍數積分活動，有特殊挑戰，有排行榜，詳情可以入去網望下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1Ts4RO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1Ts4RO.png&h=a495f2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vz4nDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vz4nDu.png&h=c99c0c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基於小弟資源有限，現時只係整左個電腦版網站，手機版可能會有移位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦想用季前賽黎做下測試，如果發現有Bug，請大家多多見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔使錢又過到癮，大家支持下，一齊玩先開心架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後大家覺得OK好玩既，分享比身邊鐘意睇波既朋友，同埋歡迎入去禁杯咖啡支持下小弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b49ab21c0ab469b4d3a4f498a11b1cd293d84","tid":2321542,"uid":353256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"有無興趣整埋足球"},{"pid":"dbdacbdfa774ab3debc6f461461199313891f7a9","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"877b49ab21c0ab469b4d3a4f498a11b1cd293d84","tid":2321542,"uid":353256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"有無興趣整埋足球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"都有, 睇下大家反應如何先再決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153a31c96df6bc75fd0d502ca2fc2f02cff63d34","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"輕輕力推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb42202fa60e64ca7d6367e9698b0161b5650df","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"輕輕力推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217916f578c384325b80d270aac326fde6d19946","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"輕輕力推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949518d178b878f6d94dc8d854a79c62cd8dd870","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:06:34.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a2012765478521474bbd7f172813bf146a8b89","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf0c36809cf29f5d29746b366b31da639bd174e","tid":2321542,"uid":387162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀推呀推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7597a2fb33ec01f0c122ba8